Interface IBoundingBox

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractReferenceGlyph, CompartmentGlyph, GeneralGlyph, GraphicalObject, LineEnding, ReactionGlyph, ReferenceGlyph, SpeciesGlyph, SpeciesReferenceGlyph, TextGlyph

    public interface IBoundingBox
    Defines classes that are inside a BoundingBox, which specifies the position and the size of the object.
